commit.message: webhook plugin now just sends the raw stuff.
increase extra cltv delta to 576 because acinq has too big delays on their channels.
finish some missing stuff on lnurl server.
fix timeout and panic when unexpected things happen.

migrate jqmethods to new design.

plus variadic arguments.
gjson Params and publish plugin docs.
AES codes and many other fixes on lnurl server.
colorize plugin prefixes based on their names.
add hmac verification of path params.
fix many things on lnurl server.
fix a math error with maxfeepercent.

description_hash-related rpc commands.

on sparko, gentlydecodepay decodes invoices with description_hash
  without having to be passed the description preimage.
on lnurl, lnurldecodepay does the same as above.
on lnurl, lnurlinvoice generates invoices with description_hash.

payment code now uses ln-decodepay.

because c-ligntning's decodepay doesn't like
description_hash.
rearrange a bunch of things and hopefully fix many vulnerabilities.
